Package: vaschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Virginia School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school enrollment data from the Virginia
    Department of Education (VDOE). Provides functions for fetching Fall
    Membership enrollment data via the Urban Institute's Education Data Portal
    API and transforming it into tidy format for analysis. Supports data from
    1987-2023 covering all Virginia school divisions and schools.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
